1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,120
That is the spirit

2
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,200
the youth of Dayang Village should have.

3
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,660
What high school students should look like.

4
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:17,760
Xiaofeng.

5
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,560
Buy some food for everyone

6
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,720
to improve your meals.

7
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,120
Thank you, Brother Gang.

8
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:25,520
But we don't need this much.

9
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:27,680
I saw what you were eating before.

10
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,010
Just green vegetables.

11
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,840
Take some money to improve your diet.

12
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,280
Buy some meat or something.

13
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,800
You are growing up now.

14
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:37,000
You should save it to help more people.

15
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,330
Here, distribute it to everyone. Come on.

16
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:45,800
Although the economy of Dayang Village was indeed not good before,

17
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:48,479
it has really changed a lot in the last two years.

18
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:50,920
The establishment of the foundation can help more people.

19
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,400
So it's okay.

20
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,800
Yes, stomp your feet.

21
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:08,880
Kick a bit.

22
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,720
That's the vibe of youth.

23
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:13,560
They fit well.

24
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:25,000
Okay, you guys try them on. Good.

25
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,240
Brother.

26
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:34,850
Why are you two here?

27
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,920
We...

28
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:38,480
It's a coincidence. Just a coincidence.

29
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,280
Brother.

30
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,160
When you do good deeds in the future,

31
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,520
there's no need to be secretive.

32
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,280
Exactly.

33
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,170
You saw everything?

34
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,360
If you had mentioned earlier that you were helping children,

35
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,880
we wouldn't have been angry with you.

36
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:49,680
Yeah.

37
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,040
So many children in the village can't afford school,

38
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,280
and barely have clothes to wear.

39
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:55,810
Helping them is helping ourselves, isn't it?

40
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,730
There are so many children to help.

41
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,200
Can you handle it alone?

42
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:02,960
How about we join you?

43
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,920
Right. If you don't take us with you,

44
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:06,650
you don't treat us as brothers.

45
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,250
Are you serious?

46
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:10,720
Serious.

47
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,130
We've made up our minds.

48
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,880
Then let's work together

49
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,800
to change the future of Dayang Village.

50
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,740
Seeing Xiaofeng and the others so full of energy today,

51
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,000
I realized something.

52
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,560
There is hope for them.

53
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:42,840
People in Dayang Village are trapped on this mountain.

54
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:46,920
We mine all our lives because we're poor.

55
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,800
In the end, we get sick.

56
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:53,440
We either die or get poorer.

57
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:54,960
It's a vicious cycle.

58
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,640
So to break this cycle,

59
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,200
they must study

60
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,540
and get out of here.

61
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:07,880
We started mining because we couldn't afford school.

62
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:13,080
Why didn't we meet anyone who could help us?

63
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,320
You're right,

64
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,160
Qiangzi.

65
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,399
Because that was your fate. But

66
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:23,560
I don't think it's the fate of Xiaofeng and the others.

67
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,480
Because we can help them now.

68
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:37,040
I feel really at peace now.

69
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,600
How so?

70
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:46,360
Because I found something to look forward to.

71
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,000
Their hope

72
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,400
is our hope.

73
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,460
So Xiaofeng and the others

74
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,440
will definitely get out.

75
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,000
Definitely.

76
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:12,240
I have solid proof that Xiao Tianman committed murder.

77
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:26,560
The grudge between you two all these years,

78
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,120
it's time to end it.

79
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:31,160
You are Xiao Tianman's mistress.

80
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,560
Didn't you die?

81
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,200
Believe it or not.

82
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,240
I, Jiang Xiaomei, have already died once.

83
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,960
The day he killed me,

84
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:44,040
I hid a voice recorder in his office.

85
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:47,600
All evidence of his murder is recorded on it.

86
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,360
What do you want?

87
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,240
I want revenge.

88
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,820
How do I know if you're telling the truth?

89
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,040
Tell me where the recorder is,

90
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,200
and I'll avenge you.

91
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,480
In the cabinet of his study desk.

92
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,560
I'll find the recorder.

93
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,640
Look at this batch we just dug up.

94
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,690
The purity isn't as good as before.

95
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,740
Go check it out.

96
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,840
Who is it?

97
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:56,680
Boss Gao.

98
00:06:57,200 --> 00:07:00,160
This is Mr. Gao Shan, the one I told you about.

99
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:06,560
What brings you to my humble place today?

100
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,240
I got a solid tip.

101
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,740
Before Jiang Xiaomei was killed,

102
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:15,580
she had someone buy a voice recorder in the city.

103
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,900
On the night she was murdered,

104
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:22,360
she took the recorder to Xiao Tianman's house.

105
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,820
Inside that recorder,

106
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:31,160
is evidence that Xiao Tianman killed Jiang Xiaomei.

107
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,400
It's in his study.

108
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,800
Do me a favor.

109
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,440
Steal it and give it to me.

110
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,360
Sure.

111
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,210
How much are you paying?

112
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,880
What is this?

113
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,080
We're good at stealing ore.

114
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,540
Not breaking into houses.

115
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:16,250
Don't you want to bring Xiao Tianman down too?

116
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,640
Boss Gao,

117
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:27,480
if we don't help you steal it,

118
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,020
will you stop buying our gold?

119
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,640
Not really.

120
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,919
The ledger,

121
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,250
the voice recorder,

122
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,919
are Xiao Tianman's Achilles' heel.

123
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,920
What if the content on the recorder is deleted?

124
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,100
It doesn't matter.

125
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,970
As long as we have the recorder,

126
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,720
I have a way to restore it.

127
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,000
Alright.

128
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:17,680
Mr. Gao,

129
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,720
do you have a plan?

130
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,880
I'll invite him out tomorrow.

131
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:25,920
His house will be empty then.

132
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:29,000
You take the chance to get the recorder.

133
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,360
I'll try to stall him

134
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,730
until you get the recorder.

135
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,680
Send me a message then.

136
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,810
That will be the signal.

137
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:44,200
The rest is up to you.
